===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

#<!--DefA--> {{uncountable}} The act or process of [[build]]ing.
#: ''The '''building''' of the bridge will be completed in a couple of weeks.''
#<!--DefB--> A closed [[structure]] with [[wall]]s and a [[roof]].
#: ''My sister lives in that apartment '''building'''.''

